 \frac{1\cdot3\cdot5\cdot \ldots \cdot (2n-1)}{1\cdot2\cdot3\cdot\ldots\cdot n} \leq 2^n  
n
P_1
P_k
P_{k+1} = \frac{1\cdot3\cdot5\cdot \ldots \cdot (2k-1)\cdot(2k+1)}{1\cdot2\cdot3\cdot\ldots\cdot k \cdot (k+1)} = \frac{1\cdot3\cdot5\cdot \ldots \cdot (2k-1)}{1\cdot2\cdot3\cdot\ldots\cdot k}\cdot \frac{2k+1}{k+1} \leq 2^k \cdot\frac{2k+1}{k+1} \leq 2^{k+1}\cdot \frac{2k+1}{k+1}
P_k
\frac{2k+1}{k+1}
\dfrac{2k+1}{k+1} \leq 2
\frac{1 \cdot 3 \cdots (2n-1)}{n!} = \frac{(2n)!}{2^n(n!)^2}
2^{2n} \ge \frac{(2n)!}{(n!)^2} = \dbinom{2n}{n}
2^{2n} = \sum_{k = 0}^{2n} \dbinom{2n}k > \dbinom{2n}n
2
P_{k + 1} = P_k \cdot \frac{2k + 1}{k + 1}
P_k \le 2^k
\frac{2k + 1}{k + 1} \le 2
k \ge 0
P_{k + 1} \le 2^k \cdot 2
